Author: RedditRabbitt
Text: Try seeing an online doctor! I was so terrified for getting treated for depression and anxiety! But knowing I could just ditch the doc in one click if I needed to was oddly comforting :)

Author: lavendermyth
Text: if your GP doesn't take your concerns seriously they either aren't a good doctor or aren't knowledgeable enough about EDs to help. plenty of people get treatment/help while not being underweight, and any medical professional that tries to deny you that help just because of your weight is incompetent.   basically, it's still worth trying but if they aren't helpful that isn't a reflection on you.
